{"tid":2017184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"120萬，就係助長每年殺6千動物","createTime":"2020-05-15T03:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T03:02:49.000Z","uid":276108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"983bf5f64d9719384bb558ef0e09ca3579ea021c","tid":2017184,"uid":276108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:02:49.000Z","msg":"今日毛ee提出要減漁農處百二萬人道毀滅經費<br />\n因為依38票反對既建制派，所以今日成功批左百二萬比漁農處，助長佢地每4日就去殺狗同其他冇人領養動物，一年殺高達6,366隻<br />\n見到真係好撚嬲，你個38票人渣垃圾死全家啦！<br />\n各位立法會準備來臨，大家一票好重要，一個有良心定冇良心既議員，大家有眼睇，各位要投下神聖誕票<br />\n<br />\n石禮謙、張宇人、林健鋒、黃定光、李慧琼、陳健波、何俊賢、易志明、姚思榮、馬逢國、張華峰、廖長江、潘兆平、盧偉國、吳永嘉、何啟明、周浩鼎、邵家輝、陳振英、陸頌雄、劉國勳、劉業強、謝偉銓、梁美芬、黃國健、葉劉淑儀、謝偉俊、陳恆鑌、梁志祥、麥美娟、郭偉強、葛珮帆、蔣麗芸、何君堯、柯創盛、容海恩、張國鈞、鄭泳舜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/petform/%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/detail/1_60940191/%E3%80%90%E6%9F%93%E8%A1%80%E4%B8%80%E7%A5%A8%E3%80%9138%E5%90%8D%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%89%8A%E6%B8%9B%E6%BC%81%E8%AD%B7%E7%BD%B2%E3%80%8C%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E3%80%8D%20%E6%AF%9B%E5%AD%9F%E9%9D%9C%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9%E3%80%8C%E8%88%87%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E7%82%BA%E6%95%B5%E3%80%8D?utm_campaign=hkad_social_ApplePetform&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=square_link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fpetform%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C%2Fdetail%2F1_60940191%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%259F%2593%25E8%25A1%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E3%2580%259138%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%2589%258A%25E6%25B8%259B%25E6%25BC%2581%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25AC%2580%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E3%2580%258D%2520%25E6%25AF%259B%25E5%25AD%259F%25E9%259D%259C%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%2589%25B9%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2595%25B5%25E3%2580%258D%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_ApplePetf